cabbage tree
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number: 1
Definition:One of the species <i>Cordyline</i> especially <i>Cordyline australis</i>, a nectar-bearing native tree, known as ti, valued by early apiarists, and early shepherds for boundary-keeping purposes.
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Flag: Farm Words
Domain:Rural
Region:[none]
